name: Collect more food
description:
A simple classic game in which you try to collect as much food as possible into a basket, but you don't control the basket as usual, here you have to move different falling food. 

So try it, share your feedback and best scores in the comments below and have fun!

Controls

You have to move the food using the "A" and "D" buttons or the corresponding arrow keys, etc. The basket you are trying to put food in will also move. You lose if the food is not in the basket five times.
